INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(110, 2, '2013-04-30 06:36:22', '2013-04-30 06:36:22', '<h1>Amputation Injury Settlements</h1>\n\nIf you have suffered injuries from a construction accident, auto accident or any other accident that resulted in amputation or dismemberment, you will need the assistance of an experienced amputation injury lawyer to represent you in your case. The Law Office of David Azizi has extensive experience in the litigation of cases wherein the client has sustained amputation or dismemberment injuries. Amputation accidents can be physically and emotionally devastating as well as leaving you and your family in a state of financial hardship. We specialize in serious personal injury cases and know what it takes litigate cases in order to recover the maximum settlement or verdict possible.\n\n<h3>When to Pursue an Amputation Injury Lawyer</h3>\n\nAny type of accident can be a traumatic experience, but when an amputation is required as a result of someone else’s negligence, you have certain rights that can help you recover compensation for damages sustained. The common types of amputation or dismemberment injuries occur when:\nYou have lost an arm, leg, hand or foot in an auto accident\nYou have lost a limb from a construction accident\nYou have lost a limb as a result of negligence on private or public property\nYou have had to undergo amputation from malpractive by a surgeon\nYou have suffered injuries and a loss of a limb from machines or equipment at work\n\nAn amputation is a form of a catastrophic personal injury and these cases cannot be taken lightly. At the Law Office of David Azizi, we take the time to conduct a full assessment of your case in order to build a solid claim against the offending party.\n\n<h3>Working with an Amputation Injury Lawyer</h3>\n\nWe know how challenging it can be to be responsible for rising medical costs, not being able to return to work or having to manage the emotional repercussions of a traumatic accident. This is why our experienced amputation lawyers will do everything legally possible to investigate your case so that you can receive the compensation you deserve. We will contact witnesses, get in touch with medical professionals and forecast the future costs of managing your medical and healthcare expenses so that we can fight for the appropriate amount of damages for your specific case.\n\nThe team of legal professionals at AziziPersonalInjury.com will not charge you any fees until your case is resolved. We are dedicated to helping you with your claim. Contact us today at (800) 991-LAW2 so that we can provide you with immediate assistance.', 'Amputation Injury', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'amputation-injury', '', '', '2013-04-30 06:36:22', '2013-04-30 06:36:22', '', 0, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/main/main/?page_id=110', 0, 'page', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(114, 2, '2013-04-30 06:37:22', '2013-04-30 06:37:22', '<h1>Bicycle and Bike Accidents</h1>\nAlmost every Vehicle Code in the country states that bicyclists have the same rights and responsibilities as a driver of a motor vehicle. However, many motorists do not realize how easy it is to run into a bicyclist. Bicycle accidents can occur at any time. The majority of bicycle accidents occur in a bike lane, crosswalk, or when a car or truck makes a turn without checking their blind spot. A bicycle accident or a bicycle-car crash can be serious and you will need the advice of an experienced bicycle accident lawyer from the Law Office of David Azizi.\n\n<h3>Why Do You Need a Personal Injury Lawyer for a Bicycle Accident?</h3>\n\nAWhen you have been badly injured as a result of a bicycle accident, you need the assistance of a personal injury lawyer to help you receive the compensation you deserve for damages you have sustained. While some people suffer serious injuries at the scene of the accident, many suffer from ongoing pain and health problems weeks, even months after the bike accident occurred. In all of these cases, a personal injury attorney from the Law Offices of David Azizi can help you receive the appropriate compensation you deserve.\n\nA bicycle or bike accident can produce serious injuries, and you may need the assistance of an experienced personal injury attorney to receive full compensation for any lost wages, medical expenses and other related costs. The professionals at AziziPersonalInjury.com specialize in road accidents case\n\nYou need the assistance of a strong and experienced attorney to present your case after a bicycle accident, and we will always look out for your best interests.\n\n<h3>How Azizi Personal Injury Will Manage Your Bike Accident Case</h3>\n\nOur firm gets involved in building a solid case by reviewing police reports, interviewing witnesses, conducting scene investigations, retaining the appropriate experts, and conducting the necessary discovery. Even though you can manage these tasks on your own, our experienced attorneys can speed up the process and make sure all of the facts surrounding your case are covered.\n\nContact us as soon as possible so we can take a close look at your case ad to help you get started on a successful recovery. Bicycle and bike accidents can take their toll on your physical and emotional health for several years after the event, so it’s important to work with an experienced personal injury attorney from the Law Offices of David Azizi. ', 'Bicycle and Bike Accidents', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bike-accidents', '', '', '2013-04-30 06:37:22', '2013-04-30 06:37:22', '', 0, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/main/main/?page_id=114', 0, 'page', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(116, 2, '2013-04-30 06:38:46', '2013-04-30 06:38:46', '<h1>Brain Injury Lawyers in Los Angeles and California</h1>\nIf you or a family member has suffered from a brain injury as a result of an accident or other catastrophic event, you will need the assistance of an experienced personal injury lawyer from the Law Offices of David Azizi to handle the case. The effects of brain injuries can last for years, even decades, and you may be responsible for expensive medical bills, counseling and other health care cost. AzizPersonalInjuyr.com can help you litigate your brain injury case and ensure that you receive the appropriate compensation for damages which you deserve.\n\n<h3>Why Work with a Brain Injury Lawyer? </h3>\n\nDealing with traumatic brain injury can be a complicated process, and most health care providers do not have the resources to cover all of the recovery and rehabilitation costs involved. Victims of a brain injury, their families and/or caregivers need specialized legal representation to assist them in litigating a solid case against the offending negligent party. AziziPersonalInjury.com can help you with every stage of this process, and our lawyers have extensive experience in the field to represent your interest vigorously.\n\n<h3>What are the Symptoms of Brain Injury? </h3>\n\nMany symptoms of brain injury do not show up for several weeks or months after the initial accident or event, so it is important to recognize the symptoms as soon as they begin to interfere with day-to-day life activities. When brain functions are disrupted, the individual may experience:\nDisturbed sleep patterns\nSlowed or impaired thinking\nDifficulty concentrating\nMemory lapses\nFaulty judgement\nPeriods of depression\n\n\nIn many cases, the individual will need to undergo cognitive and neurological testing to find out how severe the brain injury is, and what parts of the brain have been damaged.\n\nAll of these effects and the medical care that the individual needs must be taken on by the patient or their families. This financial burden may be reduced with the help of a personal injury attorney from AzizPersonalInjury.com; our firm will do everything possible to keep the client’s best interests in mind, and do the work necessary to build a solid case.\n\n<h3>How the Law Office of David Azizi Can Assist You with your Brain Injury Case? </h3>\n\nAt AziziPersonalInjury.com, we offer a free, no obligation initial consultation. If we accept your case, we will not charge you until the case has been resolved. ', 'Brain Injury Lawyers in Los Angeles and California', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'brain-injury', '', '', '2013-04-30 06:38:46', '2013-04-30 06:38:46', '', 0, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/main/main/?page_id=116', 0, 'page', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(120, 2, '2013-04-30 06:40:25', '2013-04-30 06:40:25', '<h1>Burn, Fire &amp; Explosion Injuries</h1>\nIf you have suffered from burn, fire or explosion injuries as a result of an accident, you may be eligible to receive compensation for your damages from the negligent party. Burn injuries that are the result of a fire or explosion can be very serious and require intensive medical care including but not limited to outpatient treatment from physicians, dermatologists and physical rehabilitation centers. The Law Office of David Azizi has extensive experience in handling burn injury cases.\n\n<h3>Burn Injury Cases </h3>\n\nNearly 2.4 million burn injuries are reported every year in the United States, and 75,000 of those injuries required hospitalization in the last year. Burn victims not only suffer from the immediate pain but also suffer from many emotional issues as a result of the traumatic experience. A burn injury can be a physically and emotionally devastating experience. These complex cases often require the case to be handled by an experienced personal injury attorney.\n\nSince there are several factors involved in determining the severity of the burn, determining if the injury was a result of negligence as well as finding out if the burns will create lifelong problems for the individual, you will need an experienced and knowledgeable burn injury lawyer to represent you. The Law Offices of David Azizi will take the time to assess your specific case and determine what the best course of action for your case will be.\n\n<h3>Fire Injury and Explosion Injury Cases </h3>\n\nIn addition to sustaining burn injuries from an accident, many people are injured from heat inhalation, systemic toxins in the environment and smoke inhalation. Negligence is the most common reason for fires and explosions.\n\n<h3>How a Burn Injury Lawyer Can Help You? </h3>\n\nAn experienced burn injury attorney from AziziPersonalInjury.com can determine the scope of damages sustained by victims of fire and explosion accidents. We understand that in addition to the physical injuries sustained, a burn victim also suffers from depression, mental anguish, post traumatic disorder and embarrassment.\n\nOur firm will always look out for your best interests and make sure we recover for both your physical and emotional injuries. At AziziPersonalInjury.com, we do not charge you until we recover on your behalf. We are committed to helping you receive compensation from damages from your burn, fire and explosion injury case. Contact us as soon as possible so that we may provide you immediate assistance.', 'Burn, Fire, and Explosion Injuries', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'burn-fire-and-explosion-injuries', '', '', '2013-04-30 06:40:25', '2013-04-30 06:40:25', '', 0, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/main/main/?page_id=120', 0, 'page', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(122, 2, '2013-04-30 06:41:17', '2013-04-30 06:41:17', '<h1>Bus Accidents</h1>\nIf you have suffered serious injuries after being struck by a bus or been involved in a collision with a bus, you will need legal representation from an experienced personal injury lawyer. The Law Offices of David Azizi has extensive experience in representing clients involved in bus accidents and has helped many clients recover appropriate compensation for their damages.\n\n<h3>When to Contact a Bus Accident Lawyer </h3>\n\nA bus accident or crash that involves heavy vehicles can result in serious injuries for all parties involved, and the number of bus-related accidents and injuries continues to rise in high-traffic areas around California. You will need the assistance of an experienced bus accident lawyer if you or a loved one has been involved in any of the following bus accidents including but not limited to:\nSchool bus crashes\nRiding in a bus that collided with private or public property\nNegligent driving by a bus driver\nPoor road conditions that caused a bus accident\nDangerous weather conditions that resulted in a bus accident\nWaalking in a pedestrian crossing and getting struck by a bus\nCar and bus collitions\n\nVictims of bus accidents can suffer extensive injuries including paralysis, burns, head trauma and broken bones. These circumstances often require both short-term and long-term medical care resulting in extensive medical bills, surgery, therapy and other specialized care.\n\n<h3>Working with a Bus Accident Attorney </h3>\n\nThe Law Office of David Azizi has provided aggressive and professional legal services to clients in the field of personal injury for many years and helped our clients receive the compensation they deserve. Bus accidents can be a very distressing event and often involve a great deal of physical and emotional pain and suffering. You may be suffering from broken bones, severe muscle and joint pain, or even head injuries